{"service_name": "INFOSEC Accreditation Decision Support", "service_id": "5525934971027456", "company_name": "Selex ES Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Selex ES Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     INFOSEC Accreditation Decision Support\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Accreditation support services to HMG staff charged with INFOSEC risk control and who report to Senior Information Risk Owners (SIROs). Using CLAS consultants, we offer comprehensive and enduring client friend decision support services. Accreditors and Risk Managers can rely on this service which yields high quality, timely and accountable decisions.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     More than 10 years\u2019 experience of accreditation decision making/governance support\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review/maintain accreditation documentation to support a positive accreditation outcome\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Accreditation Plans, Asset Registers and Risk Registers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review Accreditation deliverables from third parties including testing reports\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Accreditation Co-ordination support and production of all relevant products\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support and Security advice to Accreditors working in close collaboration\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Security advice to clients and vendors\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Liaison between Accreditors, Clients, Vendors and others to facilitate accreditation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support Business As Usual through ongoing INFOSEC review and support\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Complementary services available e.g. Penetration Test, Accreditation, Protective Monitoring\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     CLAS staff - assurance to Accreditor and SIRO decision making\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Call off arrangements to facilitate ad hoc support\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Flexible to accommodate requirements of large programmes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     All aspects of INFOSEC accommodated, technical, policy, personnel and procedural\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Can be used to support incident handling and treatment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Maximises Accreditor resource in multi project environments\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Full skills transfer encouraged to up-skill Customer\u2019s staff\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supported by In House, Risk Assessment and CHECK penetration testers\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3583 to \u00a31326 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/5525934971027456-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/5525934971027456-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/5525934971027456-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92392/5525934971027456-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      5525\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      9349\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      7102\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      7456\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Selex ES Ltd\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Alex X Jardine\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-de